&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Tech Talk #01 A webinar on &quot;Consent &amp;amp; Data&quot; -Cyber Security&amp;nbsp;Perspective&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jointly organized by&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;IEEE Education Society,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineering (IEEE) Hyderabad Section&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;in association with&amp;nbsp;Computer Society of India, Hyderabad Chapter, &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On 5&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; April 2020 (Sunday)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Abstract of&amp;nbsp; Tech Talk #01:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Consent &amp;amp; Data: A technology becomes more and more integral to everything we do, it can sometimes misuse the content the consent given for the data and this matter most to us. While data can be put to beneficial use, the unregulated and arbitrary use of data, especially personal data, has raised concerns regarding the privacy and autonomy of an individual.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Speaker&lt;/strong&gt;: &amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Shri. Anil Rachamalla.&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;An Enterprise Consulting Expert by Profession and Digital Wellbeing Expert by Passion &amp;amp; Purpose. Prior to taking up this role with End Now Foundation, Anil was an Enterprise Consulting Expert by Profession for over 24+ Years and Travelled over 16+ Countries on various job assignments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anil is an Engineer in Computer Science with M.B.A in Project Management and International Certifications in Supply Chain, Six sigma, delivered Personally Over 150+ Talks, 29 Workshops, 11 Exhibits, 14 Panel Discussions 32 FM. RadioTalk Shows and Submitted 4 Research Papers.&lt;/p&gt;
